    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your<strong> cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped basil</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) to a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>cheesy garlic mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
