        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the tortiglioni<strong> </strong>for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>tortiglioni</strong>, reserving a cup of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684229751870-x200.jpg",
