        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften and caramelise</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
