        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>aubergine ragù tortiglioni</strong> with the<strong> cheesy garlic bread </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>chopped basil</strong> and top with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
